OL,3,CWhat can the Welsh NHS learn from
OL,4,CDenmark's 'super hospital' system?
OL,6,F"One of the reasons we are happy to
OL,7,Fpay high taxes is because we have a
OL,8,Fwell running healthcare system."
OL,10,FThat's not a sentiment you are likely
OL,11,Fto hear from a voter in Wales ahead of
OL,12,Four Senedd Election. But on a visit to
OL,13,FCopenhagen this week, I wasn't
OL,14,Factually surprised when I heard it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@`O]
