OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774285870
OL,3,CWhat can the Welsh NHS learn from
OL,4,CDenmark's 'super hospital' system?
OL,6,FMy name is Hamish Auskerry, I'm a
OL,7,Freporter with ITV Wales and as part of
OL,8,Four crumbling hospitals special
OL,9,Fprogramme, I went to Denmark armed
OL,10,Fwith a camera to learn more about its
OL,11,Fhealthcare reforms over the last two
OL,12,Fdecades.
OL,14,FOn my first morning I wanted to film
OL,15,Frush hour, because in Copenhagen it
OL,16,Flooks different. On a famous city
OL,17,Fbridge called Dronning Louises Bro, I
OL,18,Fwatched hundreds of bikes pass me
OL,19,Fevery few minutes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
