FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774285870
OL,3,CWhat can the Welsh NHS learn from
OL,4,CDenmark's 'super hospital' system?
OL,6,FThe Danish parliamentary elections are
OL,7,Ftaking place next week and everywhere
OL,8,Fyou go in Copenhagen there are bright
OL,9,Fposters of various politicians' faces
OL,10,Fadorning walls, bridges and lamp posts.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for more exclusive and
OL,14,Foriginal coverage from ITV Wales, sent
OL,15,Fdirect to your inbox every Saturday
OL,16,Fmorning.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
