FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774285870
OL,3,CWhat can the Welsh NHS learn from
OL,4,CDenmark's 'super hospital' system?
OL,6,FAt the side of the road by the bridge
OL,7,FI met Nina Bonde, a Copenhagen local
OL,8,Fwho works for a Danish think tank.
OL,9,FEvery time the lights went red and a
OL,10,Fgathering of cyclists formed, she
OL,11,Fwould start what she called an
OL,12,F"elevator pitch with a difference",
OL,13,Fwhere she was encouraging people to
OL,14,Fvote for her favoured party.
OL,16,FThe subject of healthcare doesn't seem
OL,17,Fto be featuring much in the election
OL,18,Fhere, certainly compared to the debate
OL,19,Fin Wales over the future of the NHS.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@bO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
