FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774285870
OL,3,CWhat can the Welsh NHS learn from
OL,4,CDenmark's 'super hospital' system?
OL,6,FNina tells me that international wars,
OL,7,Fclimate change and the future of
OL,8,FGreenland are the big focusses. She
OL,9,Fsaid: "I think it's because we have a
OL,10,Fwell-run system, that is why health is
OL,11,Fnot as big a topic as it could have
OL,12,Fbeen in this election."
OL,14,FThere have been dramatic reforms in
OL,15,Fthe healthcare system in Denmark since
OL,16,F2007, including a very controversial
OL,17,Fmove to cut the number of acute
OL,18,Fhospitals in the country from 40 to 21.
OL,26,@qD@GOUtD@WO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
