OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774285870
OL,3,CWhat can the Welsh NHS learn from
OL,4,CDenmark's 'super hospital' system?
OL,6,FAt one of the so-called "super
OL,7,Fhospitals" created as part of those
OL,8,Freforms, I met Brian Holch Kristensen.
OL,9,FAs the Head of Innovation at
OL,10,FBisbepjerg Hospital, he and his team
OL,11,Fwork with expert clinicians to
OL,12,Fdetermine what their needs are.
OL,13,FTogether they try to find solutions
OL,14,Fwithin the confines of what is
OL,15,Fachievable in the buildings they have.
OL,17,F"There's a lot of clinical need that
OL,18,Fdoesn't come to the surface, we try to
OL,19,Fbring it to the surface," Brian tells
OL,20,Fme.
OL,26,@nD@YOUoD@JO]yD@AOU{D@YO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774285870
OL,3,CWhat can the Welsh NHS learn from
OL,4,CDenmark's 'super hospital' system?
OL,6,FThe reforms in the 2000s centralised
OL,7,Fexpertise in a lot of clinical areas.
OL,8,FOne of the drivers of the overall
OL,9,Freform was long cancer treatment
OL,10,Fwaiting times and the government hoped
OL,11,Fif fewer places offered cancer
OL,12,Ftreatment, the hubs of expertise
OL,13,Fremaining would perform much better.
OL,15,F"I would say the treatment of the
OL,16,Fpatients is much better now," Brian
OL,17,Fsays. "What we're trying to fix now is
OL,18,Fmaking sure everybody gets the same
OL,19,Fstandard, independent of where you
OL,20,Flive.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@]O]yD@GOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
