PN,46208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774285870
OL,3,CWhat can the Welsh NHS learn from
OL,4,CDenmark's 'super hospital' system?
OL,6,F"It turns out that in Denmark we have
OL,7,Fa lot of inequalities depending on
OL,8,Fwhere you live, so we are very good at
OL,9,Fsome places and we can be better than
OL,10,Fother places."
OL,12,FWelsh expat Geraint Dirksen-Nott feels
OL,13,Fwell served where he lives in the
OL,14,Fcapital, Copenhagen. Before I meet
OL,15,Fhim, I went up to the top of a
OL,16,Fskyscraper that's part of the
OL,17,FUniversity of Copenhagen. From the
OL,18,F15th floor it's hard not to be struck
OL,19,Fby the enormous expanse of the
OL,20,FRigshospitalet, the city's main
OL,21,Fhospital.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
