OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774285870
OL,3,CWhat can the Welsh NHS learn from
OL,4,CDenmark's 'super hospital' system?
OL,6,FIts state of the art extension, the
OL,7,FNorth Wing, dominates the skyline of
OL,8,Fthe nearby park where Geraint tells me
OL,9,Fabout growing up in Mold, Flintshire.
OL,10,FHe moved here seven years ago for work
OL,11,Fand after marrying a Danish woman,
OL,12,Fthey had a daughter. Like around 5,000
OL,13,Fother babies every year, she was born
OL,14,Fin the Rigshospitalet.
OL,16,F"It's not perfect and there are still
OL,17,Fsome issues that will probably need a
OL,18,Flong time to sort out here," he tells
OL,19,Fme.
OL,26,@xD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774285870
OL,3,CWhat can the Welsh NHS learn from
OL,4,CDenmark's 'super hospital' system?
OL,6,F"But as a relatively small country on
OL,7,Fa global scale, I think Denmark is
OL,8,Fdoing a lot of good things right."
OL,10,FDoes he think Wales could achieve
OL,11,Fsomething similar, in terms of an
OL,12,Foverall improved healthcare system and
OL,13,Fbetter patient satisfaction?
OL,15,FHe said: "I think it goes beyond just
OL,16,Fthe NHS. Here in Denmark we have
OL,17,Frainbow coalition style government.
OL,18,FThere's multiple parties with
OL,19,Fdifferent inputs and views. They
OL,20,Frepresent different voices.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@bO]wD@JOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774285870
OL,3,CWhat can the Welsh NHS learn from
OL,4,CDenmark's 'super hospital' system?
OL,6,F"Maybe in Wales if there is a broader
OL,7,Funderstanding across the political
OL,8,Fspectrum where they engage more with
OL,9,Fthe people and what they need and then
OL,10,Factually fund the NHS correctly in a
OL,11,Fmore direct way, then I think there's
OL,12,Falways that possibility."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@YO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
