OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1774285870
OL,3,CWhat can the Welsh NHS learn from
OL,4,CDenmark's 'super hospital' system?
OL,6,FThe varied, complex and unique
OL,7,Fchallenges in Welsh healthcare will
OL,8,Fnaturally require different solutions
OL,9,Fto those that have been tried in
OL,10,FDenmark. But perhaps as politicians
OL,11,Fhere search for a way to offer hope to
OL,12,Fpeople in May's Senedd Election, there
OL,13,Fmay be elements of the Danish
OL,14,Fexperience in recent years that could
OL,15,Fprovide some inspiration.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
